{"product_id":"naif-easy-styling-hair-lotion-for-baby-kids-150ml","title":"NAIF Easy Styling Hair Lotion for Baby \u0026 Kids 150ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eA hair lotion to tame and take care of wild kids hair. Naïf's Easy Styling Hair Lotion makes combing easier and reduces tangles and frizz for all hair types. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHair lotion with natural ingredients that doesn't make the hair greasy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eSoftens knots and tangles in the hair and reduces frizz in curls\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eCan also be used with cradle cap\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eFor use on babies and children, for all hairtypes\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eDoes not contain microplastics, mineral oils, SLES or silicones\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eSpray on towel-dried hair from 30 cm away. Massage gently, comb through the hair and style. Suitable for daily use.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua\/Water, Methylpropanediol, Caprylyl\/Capryl Glucoside, Glycerin, Gossypium Hirsutum (Cotton Seed) Extract, Caprylyl Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Inulin, Betaine, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Polyglyceryl-6 Oleate, Sodium Surfactin, Parfum\/Fragrance (allergen-free), Lactic Acid, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBottle made from recycled plastic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446066323783,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-easy-styling-hair-lotion-for-baby-kids-150ml-404694.png?v=1739897336","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/naif-easy-styling-hair-lotion-for-baby-kids-150ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}